This contains material for the online class "Introduction to Sociology" by Mitchell Duneier.
The course is available at www.coursera.org/course/soc101
It is for a duration of 6 weeks. It started on 11th June 2012.
Every week there is a lecture and some assigned readings. Also there will be discussion seminars via Hangout on Air.

(C) The copyright of the readings are with the respective authors.
You can use it for your private study if you are enrolled in the course. 
Enroll yourself at class.coursera.org/class/soc101
